msgid "<span class=\"d-inline-block mb-4\"><b>From $14,000</b></span>"
msgstr "<span class=\"d-inline-block mb-4\"><b>Vanaf $ 14.000</b></span>"

#. module: theme_vehicle
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_vehicle.configurator_s_three_columns
msgid "<span class=\"d-inline-block mb-4\"><b>From $19,000</b></span>"
msgstr "<span class=\"d-inline-block mb-4\"><b>Vanaf $ 19.000</b></span>"

#. module: theme_vehicle
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_vehicle.configurator_s_three_columns
msgid "<span class=\"d-inline-block mb-4\"><b>From $25,000</b></span>"
msgstr "<span class=\"d-inline-block mb-4\"><b>Vanaf $ 25.000</b></span>"

#. module: theme_vehicle
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_vehicle.s_picture
msgid ""
"<span class=\"text-o-color-3\">Our uniquely designed LED headlights are not "
"only gorgeous but powerfully light your way.</span>"
msgstr ""
"<span class=\"text-o-color-3\">Onze uniek ontworpen LED-koplampen zijn niet "
"alleen prachtig, maar verlichten ook krachtig je weg.</span>"

#. module: theme_vehicle
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_vehicle.s_three_columns
msgid ""
"A bold statement in every detail, the Koran X captures the spirit of modern "
"adventure. Built for those who refuse to compromise on performance and style."
msgstr ""
"De Koran X is een gedurfd statement in elk detail en weerspiegelt de geest "
"van het moderne avontuur. Gebouwd voor iedereen die weigert compromissen te "
"sluiten op het gebied van prestaties en stijl."

#. module: theme_vehicle
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_vehicle.s_title
msgid "All our models"
msgstr "Al onze modellen"

#. module: theme_vehicle
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_vehicle.s_picture
msgid ""
"Bring the KORAN to life on your smartphone or tablet so you can visualise it "
"for yourself"
msgstr ""
"Breng de KORAN tot leven op je smartphone of tablet zodat je hem zelf kunt "
"visualiseren"

#. module: theme_vehicle
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_vehicle.s_numbers_charts
msgid ""
"Clients saved $2.4 billion by choosing our eco-efficient and cost-effective "
"vehicles."
msgstr ""
"Klanten hebben $2,4 miljard bespaard door te kiezen voor onze eco-efficiënte "
"en kosteneffectieve voertuigen."

#. module: theme_vehicle
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_vehicle.s_three_columns
msgid ""
"Designed for the thrill-seeker, the Koran GT brings race-inspired "
"performance to the streets. Precision-tuned for speed, it promises an "
"driving experience."
msgstr ""
"De Koran GT is ontworpen voor de sensatiezoeker en brengt op races "
"geïnspireerde prestaties op straat. Hij is nauwkeurig afgestemd op snelheid "
"en belooft een geweldige rijervaring."

#. module: theme_vehicle
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_vehicle.s_key_images
msgid "Discover Excellence in Luxury Vehicle Care"
msgstr "Ontdek uitmuntendheid in onderhoud van luxe voertuigen"

#. module: theme_vehicle
#: model:ir.model.fields,field_description:theme_vehicle.field_theme_utils__display_name
msgid "Display Name"
msgstr "Schermnaam"

#. module: theme_vehicle
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_vehicle.s_key_images
